# Trend Forecasts + Reports

**Look into The Future of Color**

The color landscape is constantly evolving. Our color trend books address the influences that will affect color in tomorrow’s world, and provide an overarching color viewpoint 6 - 24 months ahead of the season. Combining visual inspiration with supporting color themes, color palettes and suggested color harmonies, we provide an in-depth analysis of emerging color stories, explain why they are relevant now, and how they can be applied to your brand and products.

![](https://www.pantone.com/media/wysiwyg/color-trends-education-pantoneview-colour-planner-2024.webp?auto=webp&format=pjpg&quality=85)

PANTONEVIEW Colour Planner

**This semi-annual lifestyle forecast takes a macro look at global color and trend 24 months ahead of the season for mens, womens, active, color cosmetics, interiors, industrial and multi-media design.**

- Each forecast designates a seasonal theme emblematic of the macro trend
- Each individual color trend palette is supported by a trend story, aesthetically provocative visual inspiration, suggested color combinations, material and product application and surface and finish direction
- Packaged with 1” x 4” swatches of each of the forecasted shades
- Includes a USB drive with digital content: static images, supported by themed movie with music, for use in creating internal story boards

[Buy Now](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books/pantoneview-colour-planner-spring-summer-2026) [View All](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books)

* * *

PANTONEVIEW Home + Interiors

**This annual forecast provides focused color trend direction for home product and interior designers 15 months ahead.**

- Each forecast highlights an over-arching theme
- Each color trend palette is supported by a trend story, culturally relevant visual inspiration, suggested color combinations, material and product application and surface and finish direction.
- Highlights key material and finishes
- Provides a comprehensive overview by color family.
- Available on its own, with 1” x 4” swatches in each of the forecasted shades
- Includes digital content: static images, photos from individual trend palettes, for use in internal story boards

[Buy Now](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books/pantone-view-home-interiors-2025-with-cotton-swatch-standards) [View All](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books)

![](https://www.pantone.com/media/wysiwyg/color-trends-education-pantoneview-home-interiors-2024.webp?auto=webp&format=pjpg&quality=85)

* * *

![](https://www.pantone.com/media/wysiwyg/color-trends-education-viewpoint-colour-2024.webp?auto=webp&format=pjpg&quality=85)

VIEWPOINT COLOUR

**This unique, coffee table-style magazine is singularly devoted to color for design professionals worldwide, providing forward-thinking insight and design direction with a global perspective.**

- Each issue designates a macro theme highlighted by a supporting narrative.
- Additional features include latest color news, new color processes, materials, surface finishes and applications, historical color and color psychology.
- An ideal source of color trend direction and inspiration for graphics, fashion, and product designers.

[Buy Now](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books/viewpoint-colour-issue-15-arise) [View All](https://www.pantone.com/products/trend-books)

## Fashion Color Trend Report

The Pantone Fashion Color Trend Report puts us at the center of the fashion world twice a year with an inside look at the top fashion colors being featured on the runways.

[View Now](https://www.pantone.com/articles/fashion-color-trend-report)

* * *

Pantone Color of the Year

A color reflecting the global zeitgeist, the announcement of the Pantone Color of the Year has become a pop culture phenomenon, commanding attention from the global design community and delivering an iconic message to billions of color enthusiasts.

